Package: bathy2026
Type: Project
Title: Reproducible Workflows for Bathynomus Data Synthesis
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jeremy", "Jenrette", 
           email = "jeremy@beneaththewaves.org",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Demonstration workflows supporting the synthesis,
    visualization, and analysis of global occurrence, molecular barcode,
    and field-based relative abundance data for the deep-sea isopod genus
    Bathynomus. The repository provides versioned example scripts and
    outputs illustrating data acquisition from public repositories
    (GBIF, NCBI GenBank), standardized data cleaning, and exploratory
    visualization and modeling approaches used in the associated
    manuscript.
